title: Wildcats earn home playoff game, top Vestal, 34-27
text:
Wildcats earn home playoff game, top Vestal, 34-27 
By wbng sports October 17, 2015 Updated Oct 17, 2015 at 12:13 AM EDT 
Johnson City, NY (WBNG Binghamton) Johnson City pulled away in the second half and staved off a late Vestal rally to clinch a home sectional playoff game, beating the Golden Bears, 34-27. The two teams will play again at Johnson City in the Class A sectional semifinals.
